Date:   Fri Sep 16 22:50:38 2011 -0700

    Strip trailing whitespace
    
    Performed with: find * -type f | xargs perl -i -p -e 's{[ \t]+$}{}'
    git diff -w & git diff -b show no diffs from this change
    
