commit d77cd6cc30bd9ebaea7c3b1c97e6984844a607f9
Author: Cyril Brulebois <kibi@debian.org>
Date:   Thu Mar 3 15:50:08 2011 +0100

    Xrandr.man: Try to make some sense.
    
